### Prueba del Microservicio de Tickets
GET http://127.0.0.1:8001
Content-Type: application/json

### Listar Todos los Tickets
GET http://127.0.0.1:8001/tickets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Listar Tickets Filtrados por Estado
GET http://127.0.0.1:8001/tickets?estado=abierto
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Obtener Ticket por ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:8001/tickets/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Crear Nuevo Ticket (Gestor)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8001/tickets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_DEL_GESTOR

{
    "titulo": "Nuevo ticket de prueba",
    "descripcion": "Esta es una descripci√≥n detallada del problema que estoy experimentando"
}

### Actualizar Estado del Ticket (Admin)
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8001/tickets/1/estado
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_DEL_ADMIN

{
    "estado": "en_progreso"
}

### Asignar Ticket a Admin
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8001/tickets/1/asignar
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_DEL_ADMIN

{
    "admin_id": 3
}

### Agregar Comentario al Ticket
POST http://127.0.0.1:8001/tickets/1/comentarios
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
    "mensaje": "Este es un comentario de prueba sobre el ticket"
}

### Obtener Historial del Ticket
GET http://127.0.0.1:8001/tickets/1/historial
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI